---
title: Just Like Nonna’s Spaghetti & Meatballs 2x the delicious portions!
description: OF COURSE your nonna’s spaghetti and meatballs is the best! But does hers come right to your door, ready to roll and big enough to serve a crowd? You’ll roast up juicy beef meatballs beside seasoned zucchini. Toss spaghetti with tangy marinara, add those meatballs, sprinkle with lots of Parmesan, and serve it all with crusty garlic ciabatta.

*This recipe is double the typical servings, providing 4 servings and 8 servings for a 2 person and 4 person box respectively.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66df53b748e223afaf60f457-cfa5151c.jpeg
